   <body>
      <prereq>
         <note>This setting only disables the pop-up messages from
appearing on the display. All LCM functions are still running.</note>
      </prereq>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the main menu, select <uicontrol>Settings</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol>System</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the UP/DOWN key, select <uicontrol>LCM Alerts</uicontrol> and press the ENTER key.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Set the <uicontrol>LCM Alerts</uicontrol> setting to either <uicontrol>On</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Off</uicontrol>. Select <uicontrol>On</uicontrol> to enable the LCM alerts and <uicontrol>Off</uicontrol> to disable
the LCM alerts.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
